Depending on the isle you're shooting for, and your raid force, this may or may not be necessary.  As I'm sure you're going for the mage epic item, camping will almost be required, especially if you plan on picking up several.  This almost necessitates a multi-day raid to catch the respawns.  While I've done this, it's extremely painful.  I'll talk to you more about this in-game, as it can make or break an PoA raid. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:green;font-family:times new roman;">Jaelyn DiMathe<br>
