<br>
The Fellowship has also recently done Sky without a Necro, again up to the Keeper of Souls isle. We only did Paladin hand-ins on that island, and called the raid as raid leader had been LD for a good long time and some folks had to go - but with the force we had, I am sure we could have done that isle as well.<br>
<br>
I believe average level was around 54, but I'm not 100% sure. And we had very few deaths beyond the compulsory sacrificial ranger. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I can't speak for the islands beyond the Keeper of Souls one, but 60+ is definitely not a requirement that far.<br>
